This allows you to hold up a single plains where an opponent is thinking swords/path at worst, and allows you to stop any green or red board wipe, or survive and possibly make into an advantage any alpha strike.
It doesn't solve everything, but counteracting craterhoof and blasphemous act isn't nothing, either.
